React View --> Action --> Reducer -->Store -->REact View 


1) React View(Component) dispatch an action.
2) Action -- invokes Reducer(pure function)
3) Reducer update/create new Store based on Action types 
4) Store update  reflect back view 

Required Package 

redux 
react-redux    
redux-dev-tools-extension
>npm i redux react-redux redux-devtools-extension

1)Create React View - Component
2)create Redux Action 
3)create Reducer(pure function(state, action))
4)rootReuder.js  - for multiple reducer
5)store.js   
6)Update App.js - provide store to all required comp


